  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the clinical results and MRI imaging of autologous
      cartilage reconstructions or collagen matrix of the knee.

      There is currently little data in the literature on clinical outcomes and imaging of this
      type of lesion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
